# Microverse Project Rules

## Code Writing Policy
- **DO NOT write actual code** (React components, webpack configs, etc.)
- **ONLY provide instructions** and guidance
- User will write all code themselves
- Explain concepts, architecture, and step-by-step instructions only

## Documentation Style
- Create detailed instruction files in `docs/` folder
- Explain WHY each step is needed
- Include common pitfalls and solutions
- Reference interview questions and tradeoffs
